  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      517.6,
      516.04,
      550.08
    ],
    "text": "Five Suspects Arrested in Connection with Assault Incident Circulated on Social Media \u2013 Malabe Police",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027,
      18.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      563.73,
      529.44,
      604.61
    ],
    "text": "Malabe Police have arrested five suspects in connection with an assault on a young man near a dansala held in Malabe town on Poson Poya Day, an incident that was captured on video and widely circulated on social media.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      619.17,
      539.38,
      646.25
    ],
    "text": "Investigations were launched following a complaint received by the Malabe Police Station on 30 June 2026, leading to the arrest of the five suspects.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      660.69,
      498.58,
      673.97
    ],
    "text": "The arrested suspects are 16 and 17 years of age and are residents of the Kaduwela area.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      688.52,
      521.27,
      715.61
    ],
    "text": "Preliminary investigations have revealed that the altercation occurred when an individual attempted to join the queue from outside while people were waiting to receive meals at a rice",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      31.91,
      537.8,
      58.99
    ],
    "text": "dansala organised in Malabe town, within the Malabe Police Division. The dispute subsequently escalated into a physical assault.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      73.57,
      539.02,
      100.65
    ],
    "text": "The arrested suspects are scheduled to be produced before the Kaduwela Magistrate's Court on 1 July 2026.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      115.21,
      527.86,
      142.29
    ],
    "text": "Further investigations are being conducted by the Malabe Police to identify and apprehend the remaining suspects involved in the incident.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
